<h1>Your Text Analysis</h1>

<h2>Number of Words: <%= @analyzed_text.text.split.size %></h2>

<h2>Vowels: <%= @analyzed_text.text.scan(/[aeoui]/).count %></h2>

<h2>Consonants: <%= @analyzed_text.text.split(" ").join.scan(/[^aeiou]/).count %></h2>

<h2>Most Common Letter: <%= @array[0].upcase %>,  used <%= @array[1] %> times</h2>
